    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required level. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted because the COU is explicitly scoped to the ASTM F1717 standard compression-bending configuration, and all three primary QoIs satisfy the pre-specified quantitative acceptance criteria (absolute error < 10%, E/uval < 1.96) across all 11 validation specimens at two laboratories. Overall credibility is judged sufficient to support the Medium-risk regulatory decision. Package conforms to ProfileMinimal; cryptographic signature is pending completion of the institutional signature workflow and has not been applied to this version.",
